3G/4G/LTE Module
----------------

|Product| is equipped with a **mini-PCIe connector** that can connect to a 3G/4G module.
The customer will also need a SIM Card Holder and a 3G/4G Antenna Connector to ensure 3G/4G works on the |product|.

.. figure:: /Media/ARM/A8/AM3354/4G_module.jpeg
   :align: center
   :figclass: align-center

   *3G/4G Module*


.. figure:: /Media/ARM/A8/AM3354/4G_com.jpeg
   :align: center
   :figclass: align-center

   *SIM Card Holder and 3G/4G Antenna Connector*


.. attention::

    #) The product does not come shipped with the 3G/4G module by default.
    #) Currently, the driver available for the 3G/4G module only supports product that has Android 4.1 OS installed on it.
